<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.7.2">
<l>karuvuṭai mēkaṅkaḷ kaṇṭā luṉṉaikkaṇ ṭālokkum kaṇka</l>
<l>ḷuruvuṭai yāyula kēḻu muṇṭāka vantu piṟantāy.</l>
<l>tiruvuṭai yāḷmaṇa vāḷā tiruvaraṅ kattē kiṭantāy.</l>
<l>maruvi maṇamkamaḻ kiṉṟa mallikaip pūccūṭṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [my] eyes see a dark cloud it’s as if they see you.</l>
<l>You who came, being born with a body to consume the seven worlds,</l>
<l>You, bridegroom of Sītā, who sleeps in Holy Araṅkam,</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] adorn [you] with jasmine blossoms that,</l>
<l> strung together, emit [a sweet] fragrance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
